title: Luke Vibert SecondLife Set 2007
description:
This is my first torrent so go easy if I get it wrong :)

Luke Vibert did a set on Second Life which I didn&#039;t manange to get to, but my wonderful partner recorded the stream and I&#039;ve been listening to it ever since.  The audio is not the best quality but the tunes are awesome, I never get tired of this, and I wanted to share :)

In the torrent is the two-part stream save and a 10 minute sample from 30-40 mins into the second part of the stream save, which will give you an indication of the quality of audio and of the tunezzzz!  Also I put in here a rough mashup I did of Luke vs NiN called &#039;Its Only Luke&#039;.

This is worth a download, the quality is not terrible, its listenable, but I wouldn&#039;t use it to rip tunes.  Definitely listenable on headphones.

I didn&#039;t manage to pick all of the songs but in there is LFO and some Luke Vibert original (Homewerks), and a range of styles from acid to hip hop to drum and bass.

Mr Luke Vibert, acid house composer extraudinaire and awesome DJ :)

My outgoing bandwidth is not great so if some more fans of Mr Luke could start seeding.
